<nav class="nav" id="nav" data-screen-label="Nav"><svg class="sunmark" viewBox="0 0 32 32" aria-hidden="true"><circle class="sun-disc" cx="16" cy="16" r="10"></circle></svg><a class="wm" href="/">AMPM <small>BUILDING SERVICES</small></a><div class="links"><a href="/services/" class="">Services</a><a href="/work/" class="">Work</a><a href="/compliance/" class="">Compliance</a><a href="/about/" class="">About</a><a href="/contact/" class="">Contact</a></div><a class="phone" href="tel:03300430080">0330 043 0080</a></nav><div class="page" style="--svc: var(--m-orange);"><div class="shell"><section class="sec p-hero"><div class="reveal in"><span class="svc-bar" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span></div><div class="reveal in"><div class="kicker">Fabric &amp; Building Envelope</div></div><h1 class="reveal d1 in">Roofing</h1><p class="lede reveal d2 in">Flat and pitched roofing self-delivered, from single-ply and built-up felt to liquid systems and large-span industrial roofs. We survey, specify and replace — keeping the building weather-tight throughout and the fall-arrest detailing right.</p><div class="reveal d3 in" style="margin-top: 28px;"><a class="btn line sm" href="/contact/">Enquire about Roofing →</a></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 32px;"><div class="kicker">What we deliver</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Roofing,<br>self-delivered.</h2></div><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span><span>Scope</span></h4><ul><li>Flat roofing — single-ply, EPDM, GRP</li><li>Built-up felt systems</li><li>Liquid-applied waterproofing</li><li>Pitched roofing — slating &amp; tiling</li><li>Large-span &amp; industrial roofing</li><li>Roof refurbishment &amp; fall-arrest systems</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span><span>Standards &amp; compliance</span></h4><ul><li>BS 5534 — slating &amp; tiling</li><li>BS 6229 — flat roofs with continuously supported coverings</li><li>Building Regulations Part L (thermal)</li><li>CDM 2015 — work at height</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">FAQs</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Your questions,<br>answered.</h2></div><div class="faq reveal in"><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you replace flat roofs and re-roof while a building stays in use?</summary><p>Yes. We sequence flat-roof replacement and re-roofing to keep the building weather-tight and operational, planning access and temporary protection under CDM 2015.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Which flat-roof systems do you install?</summary><p>Single-ply, EPDM, GRP, built-up felt and liquid-applied systems, specified to BS 6229 with thermal performance to Part L and detailing matched to the building.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you fit fall-arrest and roof-access provision?</summary><p>Yes. We install fall-arrest systems, walkways and access provision as part of the roofing package, with the work-at-height plan covered under CDM 2015.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Which areas do you cover?</summary><p>London and the South East, including Sussex, Surrey, Kent, Hampshire and Berkshire.</p></details></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">Part of Fabric &amp; Building Envelope</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Explore the full<br>package.</h2></div><div class="sectorrow reveal in"><a class="sector" href="/fabric/">Fabric &amp; Building Envelope overview</a><a class="sector" href="/fabric/facade-cladding/">Façade &amp; Cladding</a><a class="sector" href="/fabric/bsa-remediation/">Building-Safety (BSA) Remediation</a><a class="sector" href="/fabric/survey-compliance/">Survey &amp; Compliance</a></div></section><section class="sec tight line-top"><div clas